My name is Montana! 🏞️ And if I’m honest, I’m still trying to figure out who I am. Others say that I’m musical, techy, insightful, and silly. I tend to agree with many of those, along with knowing I’m a(n over)thinker who doubts himself in everything. But we heal one day at a time right? 😊

Newbie, so still trying to understand the decentralized spaces of the web, but I think I’m starting to understand the appeal. Glad to be here!
